name: BioJS Example
title: BioJS package from CommonJS module installed from NPM
description: An example using a CommonJS NPM module that is part of the [BioJS registry](http://biojs.io/).  Using [4ndr01d3/biojs-vis-example](https://github.com/4ndr01d3/biojs-vis-example) BioJS visualization module and [wilzbach/biojs-io-fasta](https://github.com/wilzbach/biojs-io-fasta) io module.
